1
00:01:13,039 --> 00:01:14,720
Greetings, Heir Yuan.

2
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:16,000
I wondered who it was.

3
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,960
So it's you, little monster.

4
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:18,600
Well?

5
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:21,240
It doesn't feel good to be despised, does it?

6
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:23,320
As long as you curse Bai Manchuan a bit,

7
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:25,450
I will tell the children in the academy

8
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,200
to treat you better.

9
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,520
Well?

10
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,440
Are you mute?

11
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,000
Speak up.

12
00:01:31,600 --> 00:01:32,160
You...

13
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:36,680
Sister-in-law.

14
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,520
Who are you?

15
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:39,520
How dare someone hit me again?

16
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:40,600
Sister-in-law.

17
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:41,800
Why did I say 'again'?

18
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,930
Heir Yuan should recognize me.

19
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:44,720
You...

20
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:46,720
You are Song Xuan.

21
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:48,640
You dare to hit me here?

22
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:50,039
I want to see His Majesty.

23
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:51,920
Wh-wh-what are you doing?

24
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:52,840
Let go of me!

25
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:55,240
Do you feel accomplished bullying a child?

26
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,960
Sharp tongue.

27
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,220
Clumsy hands and feet.

28
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:04,240
Heir Yuan is here to get beaten again.

29
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:06,360
Just you wait.

30
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,280
Wait?

31
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,720
Wait for you to get beaten again?

32
00:02:09,720 --> 00:02:13,080
Bai Manchuan, don't be too arrogant.

33
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,920
Arrogant?

34
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,490
I am being arrogant.

35
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:20,360
Listen to me. If you dare touch anyone from the Bai family again,

36
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,560
don't blame me if you can't even crawl back up.

37
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,120
Get lost.

38
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:25,840
Just you wait!

39
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:26,920
Just you wait!

40
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:30,660
I didn't expect you to be so tough.

41
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,820
I learned from you.

42
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:33,760
Sister-in-law,

43
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:36,040
can I learn kung fu with you in the future?

44
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,320
Of course.

45
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:46,600
Why are you here?

46
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,680
This is the Great Sheng's literary gathering.

47
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,680
Why can't I come?

48
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,160
I came to inform you.

49
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,620
Father Emperor is unwell.

50
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:57,760
Today's gathering is cancelled.

51
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,080
Sister,

52
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:06,680
why was it so hard for you to fight Shen Qiangwei?

53
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:08,360
It's all your fault.

54
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,480
My fault?

55
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,600
If you hadn't stopped me from practicing martial arts,

56
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,880
I would have knocked that idiot Shen Qiangwei down long ago.

57
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:15,080
Yes, yes, yes.

58
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:17,360
And I wouldn't have embarrassed myself in front of the Third Prince.

59
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,240
Yes, yes, yes.

60
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:24,480
Brother, Sister, stop arguing.

61
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:26,010
Stand there and don't move.

62
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,960
How is His Majesty?

63
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:33,920
He was poisoned.

64
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:36,280
Luckily, it's a slow-acting poison.

65
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,740
It was discovered in time.

66
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,480
Who could poison the Emperor?

67
00:03:39,640 --> 00:03:41,040
We are still investigating.

68
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:44,079
A storm is coming.

69
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:57,840
Tell me, is Song Xuan more beautiful, or am I?

70
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:03,120
Speak up. Do you all want to be mutes?

71
00:04:06,720 --> 00:04:09,380
Of course you are the most beautiful, Miss Shen.

72
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:12,040
That Miss Song acts like a bandit.

73
00:04:12,600 --> 00:04:14,600
How can she compare to our Miss Shen?

74
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,440
You are as gentle as water.

75
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:18,040
If I were Mr. Bai,

76
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:20,880
I definitely wouldn't like such a fierce woman.

77
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:24,120
But the one by Manchuan's side now is Song Xuan.

78
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,360
In that case,

79
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,040
kill Song Xuan.

80
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,680
But Song Xuan's martial arts are peerless.

81
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,800
I can't kill her.

82
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:38,920
No. If the frame-up fails,

83
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,180
it will hurt Manchuan.

84
00:04:47,159 --> 00:04:47,800
Tell me,

85
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,000
what should I do?

86
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,040
What on earth can I do

87
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:51,700
to get her away from Manchuan?

88
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:54,159
Miss Shen, I don't know.

89
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,780
It doesn't matter.

90
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,880
I'll find a way.

91
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:08,960
One day, I'll make Manchuan come back to me.

92
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,440
It's so late.

93
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:18,200
Father, are you here to visit a brothel?

94
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,920
You are the daughter of Shen Zhao.

95
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:33,320
How can you come to a place like this?

96
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:36,640
You're not here to scold me today, are you, Father?

97
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:39,960
The Emperor won't last much longer.

98
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,920
The succession is imminent.

99
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:45,960
The Shen family cannot afford any more mistakes.

100
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:48,360
I'm already being watched by Prince Bulei.

101
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:51,159
The First and Second Princes died young.

102
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,600
The Third Prince is the Emperor's only son.

103
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:56,120
The throne will be his sooner or later.

104
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,920
What do you want me to do, Father?

105
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,720
Just say it.

106
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:03,840
Have Qiangwei marry the Third Prince.

107
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:06,920
Father,

108
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,040
I have a question for you.

109
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,400
I wonder if, in your heart,

110
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:17,000
you have ever considered me your own daughter for even a moment?

111
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,760
What kind of talk is that?

112
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:28,200
Don't you just want a Shen daughter in the palace?

113
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,640
Then as you wish.

114
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,840
It's her. It's really her.

115
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:50,610
No wonder the prophecy says

116
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:53,840
Bai Manchuan will help the Queen return to the grassland.

117
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:56,720
Princess, are you sure it's...

118
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,680
the little girl from the Bai family?

119
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:04,320
But if Song Xuan is protecting her,

120
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:06,320
how do we deal with that?

121
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:10,000
Leave Song Xuan to Shen Lingbo.

122
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,400
The gods have guided me.

123
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,560
As long as I steal her destiny,

124
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,560
Tuoya

125
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:38,840
will become the true Queen of the Grassland.

126
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,640
Little girl,

127
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:49,200
everything you have is just an illusion.

128
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:56,640
Soon, your destiny will be my stepping stone.

129
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,840
After the literary gathering that day,

130
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:04,680
Chuyi was bullied even worse.

131
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,760
They even threw her brush and ink into the river.

132
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:07,480
Yes.

133
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:09,640
Those noble kids throw their weight around,

134
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:11,320
and no one dares to stand up for Chuyi.

135
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:13,320
Young Master Bai cares for her so much.

136
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:14,680
If he finds out...

137
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:15,760
Alright, alright.

138
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:16,560
Stop talking.

139
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,520
Chuyi, are you okay?

140
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,320
Adai, I'm fine.

141
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:26,760
You have to tell me if you're unhappy.

142
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:28,200
I'll stay with you.

143
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:33,640
Chuyi, let me tell you a story.

144
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,840
Okay, go ahead.

145
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:37,539
No, I have to go to the academy.

146
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,720
What are you going to do there?

147
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,520
I'm going to teach

148
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,799
those arrogant brats a lesson.

149
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,920
Otherwise, they'll think the Bai family is easy to push around.

150
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,600
You can't just act rashly.

151
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:49,440
I can't just watch Chuyi get bullied.

152
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,120
If you go there like this,

153
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:52,640
it will only make Chuyi feel

154
00:08:52,640 --> 00:08:54,770
like a weakling who needs protection.

155
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,240
But Chuyi refuses to speak up.

156
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:59,080
We can't wait any longer.

157
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:01,120
If you trust me,

158
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,720
leave this to me.

159
00:09:05,280 --> 00:09:09,480
There's a wild brat in Bai Manor.

160
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:13,680
With no father and no mother.

161
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:17,880
The wild brat is an ugly brat.

162
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:22,000
No one raises her, no one cares.

163
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,680
Don't you bully Chuyi.

164
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,560
What was that?

165
00:09:27,560 --> 00:09:28,600
It hurts!

166
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:31,380
Why does a paper ball hurt so much?

167
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:36,440
If you dare talk nonsense again,

168
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:38,240
it won't be paper balls hitting your heads.
